---
title: Ras El Hanout Lamb Meatballs with Spinach Couscous & Flaked Almonds
description: Introduce your tastebuds to the incredible flavour of ras el hanout, a North African spice that really packs a punch. Sitting on a hearty bed of spinach-mint couscous and topped with Greek yoghurt, these lamb meatballs offer a depth of flavour that's sure to knock your socks off.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ras-el-hanout-lamb-meatballs-6545942c.jpg
